            <title>[LUCENE-309] [PATCH] IndexSearcher.search(query,filter,nDocs) accepts zero nDocs</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-309</link>
                <project id="12310110" key="LUCENE">Lucene - Core</project>
                        <description>&lt;p&gt;This caused an npe from the ht.top().score lateron. &lt;br/&gt;
The root cause was a bug in a test case, which took &lt;br/&gt;
more time to track down than would have been necessary &lt;br/&gt;
with the attached patch. &lt;br/&gt;
The patch throws an IllegalArgumentException for non positive nDocs. &lt;br/&gt;
All current tests pass with the patch applied. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Regards, &lt;br/&gt;
Paul&lt;/p&gt;</description>
